The paper is about a face verification model using deep convolutional neural networks (DCNNs) for mobile platforms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the design of a lightweight network, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the computational cost and privacy concerns, which could fall under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography (cs.CR), respectively. Finally, the paper proposes a novel model, which could also fall under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
